children.description: Given that Pablo wants create a new profile on Utest
Pablo open up
Pablo opens the Automation challenge page
Pablo clicks on button to start the creation of new profile

When he complying all the require steps
| name | lastName | email | month | day | year | city | zip_code | user | password |
| Pablo Andres | Hernandez | pabloneketsu@gmail.com | May | 17 | 1992 | Bogota | 110111 | The Largest Community of Testers in the World | ?8EkZ9nD/n6LDE_ |
Pablo fill
Pablo enters 'Pablo Andres' into where we write the name
Pablo enters 'Hernandez' into where we write the lastname
Pablo enters 'pabloneketsu@gmail.com' into where we write the email
Pablo clicks on where we write the month
Pablo clicks on where we write the day
Pablo clicks on where we write the year
Pablo clicks on button to go to the next step:location
Pablo enters 'Bogota' into select the city
Pablo types 'ARROW_DOWN' in select the city
Pablo types 'ENTER' in select the city
Pablo enters '110111' into write the postal code
Pablo clicks on button to go to the next step:devices
Pablo clicks on button to go to the next step:devices
Pablo enters '?8EkZ9nD/n6LDE_' into where we write the password
Pablo enters '?8EkZ9nD/n6LDE_' into where we write the confirm password
Pablo clicks on check the option one
Pablo clicks on check the option one
Pablo clicks on check the option one
Pablo clicks on button to go to the next step:last
Then the profile is create successful
